summary:
Seasoned Software Engineer with 8+ years of experience in designing and developing software applications. Proven track record in leading teams, mentoring developers, and driving software engineering initiatives. Proficient in Java, Spring Boot, Spring Security, Docker, Kubernetes, and other cloud technologies. 

Passionate about sharing knowledge, as evidenced by the creation of technical video tutorials on YouTube in multiple languages

PT-BR: https://www.youtube.com/@DevDojoBrasil
EN-US: https://www.youtube.com/@DevDojoAcademy 

And mentoring aspiring developers, privately and professionally, as displayed in the Devoteam's Java Engineer Traineeship track https://nl.devoteam.com/working-at-devoteam/young-professional-career-opportunities-in-it/java-software-engineering-traineeship/
